<item>
            <title>[HADOOP-10030] FsShell -put/copyFromLocal should support Windows local path</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HADOOP-10030</link>
                <project id="12310240" key="HADOOP">Hadoop Common</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In current trunk code, running &apos;hadoop fs -put c:\windows\path /hdfs/path&apos; will lead to an error &lt;tt&gt;put: unexpected URISyntaxException&lt;/tt&gt;. This is a regression to the 1.0 fs shell commands. FsShell put and copyFromLocal should support Windows local path formats as localSrc argument to the two commands.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
